features: Small Yet Powerful: This small desk fan features a powerful brush-less motor and high-end aerodynamic blades, so it can create up to 10.5 ft/s strong wind that you can even feel from 3 ft away; 3 optional speeds will meet your different cooling demand; excellent choice for staying cool when you are on the go

Folding and 360° Tilt Design: Uniquely designed with a folding handle, the portable mini fan can be rotated vertically 360° to enjoy the airflow in any direction and folded as small as possible to jam into bag or suitcase; it is easy to carry, store and save space, and perfect for travel, camping or bedroom

One Button Control: Design with one-button control, this little cooling fan makes it easier for you to use; short press the button to turn on the fan and switch among speed 1/2/3/off in turns, and long press to turn it off; silicone pads at the bottom of the folding hand can help the desk fan stand on the surface more stably

USB Powered: This Portable mini fan is powered by USB and supports multiple supply by power bank, car charger, laptop, wall adapter, etc; battery-free design makes it absolutely safe to use even in cars during long haul in the Sun; it equips with a self-adhesive hook, so you can stick it on the wall if you want, then hang the fan on the hook easily

Lightweight and portable: Weighs only 0.35 lb, the portable small fan is stunningly lightweight; the compact size makes it perfect to fit your backpack or any room corner without taking up much space; it is an ideal necessity no matter you are at home, office, gym, or outside for traveling, camping, hiking, etc
body.description: This portable small fan is powered by a non-detachable USB cable and has 3 adjustable powerful speeds to meet your different cooling needs. It can be folded 360°to provide cooling air circulation in any desired direction. There is a handle for easy carrying or hanging, which makes the cooling fan more compact and space-saving, and you can easily carry it anywhere. The bottom of the folding hand has a silicone pad, which can help the mini desk fan stand on the surface stably and without vibration, which is very suitable for use on the desktop or nightstand. The fan comes with a self-adhesive hook that you can stick on the wall, and hang the fan on the hook, so that it can be used as a wall mounted fan, suitable for use in the kitchen, bedroom. Customize your space and cooling the way you like it with this small portable fan. With this USB fan, you will always feel comfortable and cool anywhere anytime. Please note that the little fan doesn't have battery, it is powered by a non-detachable USB cord.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Quiet and Colorful
reviews.reviewText: This fan is good quality and very colorful. I love the colors as an added bonus. I thought the colors were going to change from one to the other on their own but that is not the case so I was a bit disappointed about that. You can select one color. I used it at night in the bedroom so it is like a nitelite. It is very convenient having the remote. Good value for the money.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Strong But Quiet
reviews.reviewText: I bought this fan for my dorm but now I wish I would have bought it sooner for my house and bigger bedroom. This fan is STRONG. The short time I tested it in my living room it felt 10x as strong compared to our $50+ standing fan.⭐️ NOISE: 5/5 for being quiet. It is not 100% silent but with how well it works and the price point I would expect it to be much louder.⭐️ LOOK: 5/5 for colorful lights, customization, and size.⭐️ OVERALL: 5/5. For the price alone with how good this fan works it is absolutely 5 stars. I cannot speak on anything long term as far and durability due to only having it for less than a week so far but if anything changes this review will be updated!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 6, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great portable fan
reviews.reviewText: This fan is light weight but powerful. The colors are fun and very pretty. Fan is extremely quiet which makes it great for any room. The remote worked great initially. However, quit eventually working. I changed the batteries but it still didn’t work. I think maybe one of my kids messed the remote up and I can’t figure out how. Good thing is the Fan has buttons on the back so all the functions still work great without it!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 20, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Nice fan, battery in remote doesn’t work after 1 day
reviews.reviewText: The fan is nice. A little bigger than I thought, but not huge. I don’t want lights on my fan, so I haven’t used them and can’t give any kind of review on that. However, my purpose in buying a remote control fan was because it was going in a difficult to reach place. So I’m not overjoyed that the remote stopped working after 1 day, requiring me to do various contortions to check the fan. I know it’s buyer beware and there’s no way of knowing how old the battery is, etc, etc…but it’s annoying anyway.Update: The new batteries didn’t help. I was able to contact the seller through Amazon, and requested a new remote. Today I received a whole new fan. Maybe they felt the problem was in the receiver for the remote and not the remote itself? Impressed with the customer service. Anyway, new fan is working fine, will be keeping my fingers crossed that the remote keeps working. 🤞🏼10-27-22Further update…the new remote also stopped working within just a few days. I appreciate that the company sent me a new fan, but maybe they should just concentrate on remaking a new and better remote. I guess I will give this fan to someone that doesn’t need one with a remote and order a new - and different brand - fan.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Made very cheap!
reviews.reviewText: I’m just updating because, I really do love this fan. I hate so much that the remote control doesn’t work though. The lights are still working!!I loved this fan! I bought 3 more for family members. So quiet, great fan power, lightweight. After 8 days of use, the remote control quit working. I replaced the battery but, it still won’t work. There are control buttons on the back of the fan, thank goodness. About a week later the light control button works about half the time, after I try a few times. No doubt that it will quit within a few days. I’m so disappointed! It would be worth the money if it worked as it should 😔I’m very surprised at the power of this little thing! It does have 3 speeds. I don’t know how I missed it the first time. The low speed is a perfect breeze for close range such as a desk.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Ideal Desk Fan
reviews.reviewText: This desk fan is perfect with the remote and it is quiet enough to answer the office phone with fan still on. I have huge windows that get a ton of sun in the afternoons. Anyone looking for a fan for your office, you can stop shopping because this one is perfect and cute.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect size for window sill
reviews.reviewText: Has a little remote so I don't have to get out of bed to adjust speed, or on/off, or colors. Perfect for a smaller window.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Good fan bad remote
reviews.reviewText: The fan itself is nice. The RGB works good and the fan give plenty of air for a 8in fan.The only issue I found which was deal breaker for me was the remote stopped working on this. I even returned one and got another but the same issue happened. It didn’t take long either. The first one fail in a day and the second took a week. I saw many others had this issue and from what I can tell the ir receiver goes bad. How I am not sure since I did not move it after I place it.
It produces strong enough wind for desk and comes with remote. One of the strongest desk fan I had seen. Good product

reviews.reviewTitle: 同商品の複数使用は、要注意。
reviews.reviewText: コンパクトで風量もそこそこで、リモコン操作ができるので、4台を各部屋用に購入。しかし、各部屋でリモコン操作をすると、4台とも一つのリモコンで同時に動いてしまうと言う問題があります。リモコンが無線方式のようで、ファン側も感度が良く、1階と２階で、8ｍ以上離れた部屋でも反応します。しかたなく、本体のスイッチで動かしています。残念な結果でした、複数のご使用は、同一場所で一斉にお使いになることをお勧めいたします。
Value for money, works as described
前回購入してよかったのでもう一個買ったら若干不良品だった気がします。スイッチオンしても１回目２回目回転してすぐに停止３回目くらいでちゃんと動くといった感じです。
